title: Jack Rhysider, Darknet Diaries [ML B-Side]
description: Darknet Diaries, Jack Rhysider's show, is the most popular cyber security podcast - and one of the most successful tech podcasts in the US in general. Eliad Kimhy spoke with Jack about the origins of Darknet Diaries, his heroes and role models, and the effect the show’s success has had on his personal life - which, you might be surprised to discover, wasn’t always 100% positive.
